.560" end="1:08.690">て</span><span begin="1:08.690" end="1:08.910">ゆ</span><span begin="1:08.910" end="1:09.050">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">渐渐焦灼</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kogashite yuku</span></p><p begin="1:09.370" end="1:11.820" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:09.370" end="1:09.580">そ</span><span begin="1:09.580" end="1:09.740">の</span><span begin="1:09.740" end="1:09.920">記</span><span begin="1:09.920" end="1:10.250">号</span><span begin="1:10.250" end="1:10.370">で</span><span begin="1:10.370" end="1:10.740">今</span><span begin="1:10.740" end="1:11.080">願</span><span begin="1:11.080" end="1:11.260">っ</span><span begin="1:11.260" end="1:11.420">て</span><span begin="1:11.420" end="1:11.820">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">现在就用那符号许愿吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono kigou de ima negatte yo</span></p><p begin="1:12.120" end="1:14.680" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:12.120" end="1:12.440">何</span><span begin="1:12.440" end="1:12.620">も</span><span begin="1:12.620" end="1:12.830">か</span><span begin="1:12.830" end="1:12.950">も</span><span begin="1:12.950" end="1:13.330">全</span><span begin="1:13.330" end="1:13.480">部</span><span begin="1:13.480" end="1:13.810">届</span><span begin="1:13.810" end="1:13.990">い</span><span begin="1:13.990" end="1:14.150">て</span><span begin="1:14.150" end="1:14.680">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">把一切都传达过来吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nanimo kamo zenbu todoite yo</span></p><p begin="1:25.880" end="1:31.220" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:25.880" end="1:26.280">言</span><span begin="1:26.280" end="1:26.500">え</span><span begin="1:26.600" end="1:27.560">な</span><span begin="1:27.560" end="1:27.640">い</span><span begin="1:27.930" end="1:28.630">表</span><span begin="1:28.630" end="1:28.880">情</span><span begin="1:29.180" end="1:29.320">を</span><span begin="1:29.320" end="1:30.320">俯</span><span begin="1:30.320" end="1:30.700">く</span><span begin="1:30.700" end="1:30.870">の</span><span begin="1:30.870" end="1:31.020">な</span><span begin="1:31.020" end="1:31.220">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果低着头掩饰无法言喻的表情</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ienai hyoujou o utsumuku no nara</span></p><p begin="1:31.700" end="1:36.420" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:31.700" end="1:32.070">人</span><span begin="1:32.070" end="1:32.370">間</span><span begin="1:32.370" end="1:32.580">じゃ</span><span begin="1:32.580" end="1:32.780">な</span><span begin="1:32.780" end="1:32.910">い</span><span begin="1:32.910" end="1:33.100">っ</span><span begin="1:33.100" end="1:33.340">て</span><span begin="1:33.750" end="1:34.110">気</span><span begin="1:34.110" end="1:34.450">づ</span><span begin="1:34.450" end="1:34.810">い</span><span begin="1:34.810" end="1:35.130">て</span><span begin="1:35.130" end="1:35.480">い</span><span begin="1:35.480" end="1:35.710">た</span><span begin="1:35.710" end="1:36.000">ん</span><span begin="1:36.000" end="1:36.130">で</span><span begin="1:36.130" end="1:36.420">しょ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">其实你已经察觉到我不是人类了吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ningen janai tte kizuite itandesho</span></p><p begin="1:36.830" end="1:39.130" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:36.830" end="1:37.020">い</span><span begin="1:37.020" end="1:37.200">が</span><span begin="1:37.200" end="1:37.340">み</span><span begin="1:37.340" end="1:37.470">合</span><span begin="1:37.470" end="1:37.710">う</span><span begin="1:37.710" end="1:37.880">の</span><span begin="1:37.880" end="1:38.010">が</span><span begin="1:38.010" end="1:38.380">正</span><span begin="1:38.380" end="1:38.740">解</span><span begin="1:38.740" end="1:38.900">な</span><span begin="1:38.900" end="1:39.130">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果互相敌视才是正确答案的话</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Igamiau no ga seikai nara</span></p><p begin="1:39.520" end="1:42.660" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:39.520" end="1:39.740">そ</span><span begin="1:39.740" end="1:39.910">の</span><span begin="1:39.910" end="1:40.040">目</span><span begin="1:40.040" end="1:40.260">澄</span><span begin="1:40.260" end="1:40.390">ま</span><span begin="1:40.390" end="1:40.580">し</span><span begin="1:40.580" end="1:40.750">て</span><span begin="1:40.750" end="1:40.920">聞</span><span begin="1:40.920" end="1:41.290">き</span><span begin="1:41.390" end="1:42.110">連</span><span begin="1:42.110" end="1:42.210">ね</span><span begin="1:42.310" end="1:42.660">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就擦亮双眼倾听并罗列出来</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono me sumashite kikitsuranete</span></p><p begin="1:44.660" end="1:46.330" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:44.660" end="1:46.330">嗚呼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">啊啊</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aa</span></p><p begin="1:47.220" end="1:50.000" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:47.220" end="1:47.580">痛</span><span begin="1:47.580" end="1:47.740">み</span><span begin="1:47.740" end="1:48.100">全</span><span begin="1:48.100" end="1:48.250">部</span><span begin="1:48.250" end="1:48.460">知</span><span begin="1:48.460" end="1:48.600">っ</span><span begin="1:48.600" end="1:48.770">て</span><span begin="1:48.770" end="1:49.160">空</span><span begin="1:49.160" end="1:49.270">を</span><span begin="1:49.270" end="1:49.620">仰</span><span begin="1:49.620" end="1:49.790">い</span><span begin="1:49.790" end="1:50.000">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">知晓全部的痛楚仰望天空</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itami zenbu shitte sora o aoide</span></p><p begin="1:50.280" end="1:52.210" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:50.280" end="1:50.450">そ</span><span begin="1:50.450" end="1:50.640">こ</span><span begin="1:50.640" end="1:50.810">か</span><span begin="1:50.810" end="1:50.960">ら</span><span begin="1:50.960" end="1:51.300">今</span><span begin="1:51.300" end="1:51.490">落</span><span begin="1:51.490" end="1:51.670">ち</span><span begin="1:51.670" end="1:51.800">る</span><span begin="1:51.800" end="1:52.030">ん</span><span begin="1:52.030" end="1:52.210">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">现在就要从那里坠落了</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Soko kara ima ochirunda</span></p><p begin="1:52.360" end="1:53.530" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:52.360" end="1:52.660">守</span><span begin="1:52.660" end="1:52.850">っ</span><span begin="1:52.850" end="1:53.000">て</span><span begin="1:53.000" end="1:53.200">く</span><span begin="1:53.200" end="1:53.340">れ</span><span begin="1:53.340" end="1:53.530">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">保护我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mamotte kure yo</span></p><p begin="1:53.710" end="1:54.830" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:53.710" end="1:53.890">磨</span><span begin="1:53.890" end="1:54.120">耗</span><span begin="1:54.120" end="1:54.400">し</span><span begin="1:54.400" end="1:54.590">て</span><span begin="1:54.590" end="1:54.700">る</span><span begin="1:54.700" end="1:54.830">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">正在磨损啊</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mamou shiteru yo</span></p><p begin="1:55.040" end="1:57.600" itunes:key="L37" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:55.040" end="1:55.260">そ</span><span begin="1:55.260" end="1:55.430">の</span><span begin="1:55.430" end="1:55.750">電</span><span begin="1:55.750" end="1:55.820">波</span><span begin="1:55.820" end="1:55.930">思</span><span begin="1:55.930" end="1:56.270">考</span><span begin="1:56.270" end="1:56.430">に</span><span begin="1:56.430" end="1:56.610">既</span><span begin="1:56.610" end="1:56.930">読</span><span begin="1:56.930" end="1:57.120">を</span><span begin="1:57.120" end="1:57.300">つ</span><span begin="1:57.300" end="1:57.470">け</span><span begin="1:57.470" end="1:57.600">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">给那电波思考标上已读</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono denpa shikou ni kidoku o tsukete</span></p><p begin="1:57.770" end="2:00.200" itunes:key="L38" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:57.770" end="1:57.980">そ</span><span begin="1:57.980" end="1:58.160">の</span><span begin="1:58.160" end="1:58.310">ま</span><span begin="1:58.310" end="1:58.500">ま</span><span begin="1:58.500" end="1:58.840">今</span><span begin="1:58.840" end="1:59.000">で</span><span begin="1:59.000" end="1:59.140">も</span><span begin="1:59.140" end="1:59.480">笑</span><span begin="1:59.480" end="1:59.680">っ</span><span begin="1:59.680" end="1:59.910">て</span><span begin="2:00.010" end="2:00.200">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就那样现在也笑一笑吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono mama ima demo waratte yo</span></p><p begin="2:00.530" end="2:03.050" itunes:key="L39" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:00.530" end="2:00.840">脳</span><span begin="2:00.840" end="2:01.220">髄</span><span begin="2:01.220" end="2:01.360">を</span><span begin="2:01.360" end="2:01.540">混</span><span begin="2:01.540" end="2:01.720">ぜ</span><span begin="2:01.720" end="2:01.870">て</span><span begin="2:01.870" end="2:02.030">揺</span><span begin="2:02.030" end="2:02.400">さ</span><span begin="2:02.400" end="2:02.590">ぶ</span><span begin="2:02.590" end="2:02.740">っ</span><span begin="2:02.740" end="2:02.900">て</span><span begin="2:02.900" end="2:03.050">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">搅乱并摇撼脑髓吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nouzui o mazete yusabutte yo</span></p><p begin="2:03.280" end="2:04.430" itunes:key="L40" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:03.280" end="2:03.590">迷</span><span begin="2:03.590" end="2:03.760">っ</span><span begin="2:03.760" end="2:03.940">て</span><span begin="2:03.940" end="2:04.080">み</span><span begin="2:04.080" end="2:04.280">せ</span><span begin="2:04.280" end="2:04.430">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">试着迷惘给我看</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mayotte misete</span></p><p begin="2:04.640" end="2:06.680" itunes:key="L41" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:04.640" end="2:04.970">届</span><span begin="2:04.970" end="2:05.140">い</span><span begin="2:05.140" end="2:05.310">て</span><span begin="2:05.310" end="2:05.450">み</span><span begin="2:05.450" end="2:05.890">せ</span><span begin="2:05.990" end="2:06.190">て</span><span begin="2:06.190" end="2:06.680">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">试着传达给我看吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Todoite misete yo</span></p><p begin="2:17.590" end="2:20.160" itunes:key="L42" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:17.590" end="2:17.780">絵</span><span begin="2:17.780" end="2:17.910">文</span><span begin="2:17.910" end="2:18.100">字</span><span begin="2:18.100" end="2:18.250">ば</span><span begin="2:18.250" end="2:18.440">か</span><span begin="2:18.440" end="2:18.600">り</span><span begin="2:18.600" end="2:18.770">で</span><span begin="2:18.770" end="2:19.270">頷</span><span begin="2:19.270" end="2:19.450">き</span><span begin="2:19.450" end="2:19.630">あ</span><span begin="2:19.630" end="2:19.770">お</span><span begin="2:19.770" end="2:19.990">う</span><span begin="2:19.990" end="2:20.160">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就只用表情符号来互相点头附和吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Emoji bakari de unazukiaou yo</span></p><p begin="2:20.460" end="2:22.840" itunes:key="L43" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:20.460" end="2:20.630">上</span><span begin="2:20.630" end="2:20.830">昇</span><span begin="2:20.830" end="2:20.980">中</span><span begin="2:20.980" end="2:21.100">の</span><span begin="2:21.100" end="2:21.180">記</span><span begin="2:21.180" end="2:21.360">号</span><span begin="2:21.360" end="2:21.500">が</span><span begin="2:21.680" end="2:21.870">今</span><span begin="2:21.870" end="2:22.000">も</span><span begin="2:22.000" end="2:22.180">鼓</span><span begin="2:22.180" end="2:22.330">動</span><span begin="2:22.330" end="2:22.450">を</span><span begin="2:22.450" end="2:22.550">止</span><span begin="2:22.550" end="2:22.610">め</span><span begin="2:22.610" end="2:22.710">る</span><span begin="2:22.710" end="2:22.840">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">正在上升的符号如今心也停止跳动了吗</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Joushou chuu no kigou ga ima mo kodou o tomeru no</span></p><p begin="2:23.180" end="2:25.420" itunes:key="L44" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:23.180" end="2:23.560">単</span><span begin="2:23.560" end="2:23.890">純</span><span begin="2:23.890" end="2:24.060">だ</span><span begin="2:24.060" end="2:24.220">と</span><span begin="2:24.220" end="2:24.410">か</span><span begin="2:24.410" end="2:24.530">言</span><span begin="2:24.530" end="2:24.660">う</span><span begin="2:24.760" end="2:24.920">の</span><span begin="2:24.920" end="2:25.080">な</span><span begin="2:25.080" end="2:25.420">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果你要说这很简单的话</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tanjun da toka iu no nara</span></p><p begin="2:25.750" end="2:28.300" itunes:key="L45" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:25.750" end="2:25.920">い</span><span begin="2:25.920" end="2:26.060">ま</span><span begin="2:26.060" end="2:26.260">す</span><span begin="2:26.260" end="2:26.390">ぐ</span><span begin="2:26.390" end="2:26.620">わ</span><span begin="2:26.620" end="2:26.780">か</span><span begin="2:26.780" end="2:26.940">り</span><span begin="2:26.940" end="2:27.110">や</span><span begin="2:27.110" end="2:27.310">す</span><span begin="2:27.310" end="2:27.380">く</span><span begin="2:27.380" end="2:27.770">教</span><span begin="2:27.770" end="2:27.980">え</span><span begin="2:27.980" end="2:28.130">て</span><span begin="2:28.130" end="2:28.300">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">现在立刻浅显易懂地告诉我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ima sugu wakariyasuku oshiete yo</span></p><p begin="2:28.620" end="2:30.750" itunes:key="L46" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:28.620" end="2:28.980">寂</span><span begin="2:28.980" end="2:29.160">し</span><span begin="2:29.160" end="2:29.360">く</span><span begin="2:29.360" end="2:29.490">な</span><span begin="2:29.490" end="2:29.660">い</span><span begin="2:29.660" end="2:29.810">よ</span><span begin="2:29.810" end="2:30.130">今</span><span begin="2:30.130" end="2:30.460">更</span><span begin="2:30.570" end="2:30.750">もう</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">已经不寂寞了哦 事到如今</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sabishikunai yo imasara mou</span></p><p begin="2:31.220" end="2:33.440" itunes:key="L47" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:31.220" end="2:31.380">い</span><span begin="2:31.380" end="2:31.540">つ</span><span begin="2:31.540" end="2:31.740">で</span><span begin="2:31.740" end="2:31.880">も</span><span begin="2:31.880" end="2:32.230">繋</span><span begin="2:32.230" end="2:32.380">が</span><span begin="2:32.380" end="2:32.570">っ</span><span begin="2:32.570" end="2:32.750">て</span><span begin="2:32.750" end="2:32.890">る</span><span begin="2:32.890" end="2:33.080">ん</span><span begin="2:33.080" end="2:33.270">だ</span><span begin="2:33.270" end="2:33.440">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无论何时都紧紧相连着哦</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itsudemo tsunagatterunda yo</span></p><p begin="2:33.610" end="2:38.880" itunes:key="L48" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:33.610" end="2:33.780">だ</span><span begin="2:33.780" end="2:33.930">か</span><span begin="2:33.930" end="2:34.040">ら</span><span begin="2:34.160" end="2:34.310">も</span><span begin="2:34.310" end="2:34.460">う</span><span begin="2:36.330" end="2:36.510">テ</span><span begin="2:36.510" end="2:36.670">レ</span><span begin="2:36.670" end="2:36.840">パ</span><span begin="2:36.840" end="2:37.180">シー</span><span begin="2:37.180" end="2:37.330">に</span><span begin="2:37.330" end="2:37.500">気</span><span begin="2:37.500" end="2:37.650">づ</span><span begin="2:37.650" end="2:37.850">い</span><span begin="2:37.850" end="2:38.010">た</span><span begin="2:38.010" end="2:38.210">振</span><span begin="2:38.210" end="2:38.370">り</span><span begin="2:38.370" end="2:38.520">し</span><span begin="2:38.520" end="2:38.720">て</span><span begin="2:38.720" end="2:38.880">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">所以就装作已经察觉到了心灵感应吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dakara mou terepashii ni kizuita furi shite yo</span></p><p begin="2:39.020" end="2:41.830" itunes:key="L49" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:39.020" end="2:39.260">そ</span><span begin="2:39.260" end="2:39.410">の</span><span begin="2:39.410" end="2:39.570">目</span><span begin="2:39.570" end="2:39.740">か</span><span begin="2:39.740" end="2:39.900">っ</span><span begin="2:39.900" end="2:40.090">ぽ</span><span begin="2:40.090" end="2:40.260">じ</span><span begin="2:40.260" end="2:40.420">っ</span><span begin="2:40.420" end="2:40.580">て</span><span begin="2:40.580" end="2:40.740">気</span><span begin="2:40.740" end="2:41.090">づ</span><span begin="2:41.090" end="2:41.280">い</span><span begin="2:41.280" end="2:41.450">た</span><span begin="2:41.450" end="2:41.830">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果你睁大眼睛察觉到了的话</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono me kappojitte kizuitara</span></p><p begin="2:42.120" end="2:45.330" itunes:key="L50" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:42.120" end="2:42.650">心</span><span begin="2:42.650" end="2:42.770">の</span><span begin="2:42.770" end="2:43.090">内</span><span begin="2:43.090" end="2:43.260">を</span><span begin="2:43.260" end="2:43.590">荒</span><span begin="2:43.590" end="2:43.830">ん</span><span begin="2:43.830" end="2:43.940">で</span><span begin="2:44.170" end="2:44.490">送</span><span begin="2:44.490" end="2:44.690">っ</span><span begin="2:44.690" end="2:44.830">て</span><span begin="2:44.830" end="2:45.020">み</span><span begin="2:45.020" end="2:45.180">て</span><span begin="2:45.180" end="2:45.330">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">就试着将这荒芜的内心发送过来吧</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kokoro no uchi o susande okutte mite yo</span></p><p begin="2:45.530" end="2:46.700" itunes:key="L51" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:45.530" end="2:45.700">飛</span><span begin="2:45.700" end="2:45.920">ば</span><span begin="2:45.920" end="2:46.050">し</s